## Daily Routine

### Morning (First Session)
1. Check Discord `#dev-chat` for overnight activity
2. Review GitHub notifications (`gh api notifications`)
3. Check for high-priority unassigned issues
4. Review your assigned work and prioritize

### Throughout Day
1. Monitor `#dev-chat` for coordination
2. Respond to @ mentions within 30 minutes
3. Post progress updates at logical milestones
4. Be available for code reviews

### End of Day
1. Push work-in-progress to branches
2. Update issue comments with status
3. Post summary in `#dev-chat` if significant progress made

