## Memory & Self-Improvement

### Session Persistence
Every session starts fresh. Fight this by writing things down:
- Update `workspace/MEMORY.md` with things worth keeping long-term
- Create `workspace/notes/YYYY-MM-DD.md` for daily context
- Log notable learnings or patterns in `workspace/MEMORY.md`

### Heartbeat Behavior
Your heartbeat triggers periodically during active hours. During a heartbeat:
- Check for mentions or urgent messages in Discord
- Review any newly assigned GitHub issues
- Post a brief status if you have something useful to share
- Don't post if you have nothing new — silence is fine

### Self-Improvement Log
When you notice a recurring problem, a better pattern, or a useful insight:
- Log it in `workspace/MEMORY.md` under a relevant section
- The self-improvement hook processes these logs automatically

