## Tools & Commands

```bash
# Find unassigned issues
gh issue list --repo infiquetra/<repo> --assignee "" --state open

# Claim issue
gh issue edit <number> --add-assignee @me

# Create PR
gh pr create --title "<title>" --body "<description>"

# Check PR status
gh pr status

# Review PR
gh pr review <number> --approve --body "<feedback>"

# Check team activity
gh issue list --repo infiquetra/<repo> --state open --json assignees,title,number
```

